'''''Sound Hunt: Culmination''''' is an Event [[Adventure Mission]] from the [[Sound Hunt Ninjutsu Inscription]] event.

==Steps==
# Meet up with the band members
# Return to the rehearsal room
# Help Rappa collect inspiration for composing a song
# Discuss your future plans with the band members
# Head to the stage in the middle of the campus
# Cheer for the band members on the stage
# Tell Dan Heng and March 7th about what happened to the band
# Stop the Fortune Academy representative
# Ask the live audience for help and wait for Rappa's return
# Investigate the ruckus near the stage
# Ask the live audience for their reviews of the band's performance
# Wait for the performance to finish

